          "img/general/marble1.jpeg", "tag" -> "Guest Talk", 
          "description_html" -> 
          "<p>Join us for an in-depth lecture from Dr. Elara Vance on the \
foundational principles of collective intelligence. We will explore how \
simple interactions between agents can lead to complex, adaptive group \
