          "img/general/marble2.jpeg", "tag" -> "Nascent Research", 
          "description_html" -> 
          "<p>Our Nascent Research series returns with three rapid-fire \
presentations on the application of network models to urban systems. Each \
speaker will have 10 minutes to present their emerging research, followed by \
